commit.message: Add links to the Homebrew and Guix packages in the README.

Sync embedded Spleen 8x16 version to Spleen 2.0.0.

This swap arrows at positions 1A and 1B in the 8x16 version.
Add initial version of Spleen 8x16, some characters are still missing.
Harmonize the line on packages availability across all projects.
Point the OpenBSD package link to openports.pl.
Move a comment to the right place, minor formatting fix.

Increment pcboard_buffer by more than one element at a time.

We now increment by PCB_BUFFER_SIZE (currently defined to 4096) when
calling reallocarray().
Remove trailing dots in the 1.2.9 release notes in ChangeLog.
List projects using libansilove in the README.
Various minor README improvements, mostly to sync with Ansilove.
Also build and install libansilove as a static library.
Add a link to the Gentoo package in the README.
Use CMAKE_C_STANDARD instead of hardcoding compiler flags.
